The paper deals with the performance of precoding in MISO broadcast channels with confidential messages, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the impact of imperfect channel state information on the system performance, which is a topic related to communication engineering (cs.CE) and networked systems (cs.NI).
